        Selling Your Brisbane Property to Move Interstate: Timing, Logistics and the Double-Settlement Challenge
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Relocating from Brisbane to Sydney, Melbourne, Perth or Adelaide forces a structural choice: sell first, buy first, or aim for a simultaneous settlement. Each path has different costs and risks.
      </p>
